metadata.name: Journey #1
metadata.description:
“Journey” continues to push the boundaries of photography and generative art as it harnesses the same on-chain randomisation mechanics as “Reflections” did.

Inspired by the unique path that we are all on as humans, “Journey” combines 60 unique layers into familiar yet dream-like landscapes all connected by a unique 'path' which leads you into the distance.

Whether a 2-lane highway or a raging river, each path leads toward a beautiful horizon under a dramatic sky to fuel a sense of wonder and awe in you, much like the feelings that are invoked for me when I travel to a new destination.
